Installing the template in dom0 fails because of a missing dependency (qubes-core-dom0-linux)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Again you built a template based on a recent Qubes API which has not
been released yet. So skip the dependency for now:

.. code:: wiki

    sudo rpm -U --nodeps yourpackage.rpm

chroot-archlinux/dev/pts has not been unmounted
-----------------------------------------------

This is a known problem when there are errors during building. Just
unmount what you can (or reboot your vm if you are too lazy :) )
